+# CLAUDE.md
+
+This file provides guidance to Claude Code when working with this codebase.
+Generated by [sourcebook](https://github.com/maroondlabs/sourcebook). Review and edit — the best context comes from human + machine together.
+
+## Commands
+
+- **Dev:** `turbo run dev --filter="@calcom/web"`
+- **Build:** `turbo run build --filter=@calcom/web...`
+- **Test:** `TZ=UTC vitest run`
+- **Lint:** `turbo lint`
+- **db-deploy:** `turbo run db-deploy`
+- **db-seed:** `turbo run db-seed`
+- **deploy:** `turbo run deploy`
+- **deploy:trigger:prod:** `turbo run deploy:trigger:prod --filter="@calcom/features"`
+- **deploy:trigger:staging:** `turbo run deploy:trigger:staging --filter="@calcom/features"`
+
+## Critical Constraints
+
+- **Testing:** Tests are co-located with source files (*.test.ts next to *.ts). Keep this pattern -- don't create a separate test/ directory.
+- **Git history:** 6 reverted commits in the last year. Previously attempted and rolled back: revert (#27933)
+- **Anti-patterns:** Tried and reverted: "revert (#27933)". This approach was explicitly rejected.
+- **Hidden dependencies:** Files that change together across directories (invisible coupling): slots.controller.e2e-spec.ts ↔ user-event-type-slots.controller.e2e-spec.ts (4 co-commits)
+- **Commit conventions:** Uses Conventional Commits (feat/fix/docs/etc). Common scopes: i18n, form-builder, deps, e2e, calendar. Follow this pattern for new commits.
+- **Core modules:** Hub files (most depended on): packages/trpc/server/types.ts (imported by 183 files); apps/web/playwright/lib/fixtures.ts (imported by 86 files); packages/platform/atoms/lib/http.ts (imported by 72 files); packages/features/di/di.ts (imported by 60 files); packages/app-store/_utils/getAppKeysFromSlug.ts (imported by 53 files). Changes here have the widest blast radius.
+- **Circular dependencies:** Circular import chains detected: bookingScenario.ts → getMockRequestDataForBooking.ts → bookingScenario.ts; create-event-type.input.ts → CantHaveRecurrenceAndBookerActiveBookingsLimit.ts → create-event-type.input.ts; handleMarkNoShow.ts → handleSendingAttendeeNoShowDataToApps.ts → handleMarkNoShow.ts. Avoid adding to these cycles.
+
+## Stack
+
+Next.js, Tailwind CSS, TypeScript
+
+## Project Structure
+
+- `scripts/` — Build / utility scripts
+- `docs/` — Documentation
+
+## Core Modules (by structural importance)
+
+- `packages/features/webhooks/lib/dto/types.ts`
+- `packages/features/webhooks/lib/interface/IWebhookRepository.ts`
+- `packages/trpc/server/types.ts`
+- `packages/platform/atoms/lib/http.ts`
+- `packages/app-store/_utils/getAppKeysFromSlug.ts`
+
+## Conventions & Patterns
+
+- **Project structure:** This is a monorepo. Changes may affect multiple packages. Check workspace dependencies before modifying shared code.
+- **Import conventions:** Project uses barrel exports (index.ts files that re-export). Import from the directory, not from deep paths.
+- **Environment:** Environment variables are documented in .env.example. Copy it to .env.local before running the project.
+- **Export conventions:** Project strongly prefers named exports over default exports. Use `export function` / `export const`, not `export default`.
+
+## Additional Context
+
+- **Environment:** 4 env vars detected. Public (browser-exposed): NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBAPP_URL. Private (server-only): CI, PLAYWRIGHT_HEADLESS, PWDEBUG.
+- **Anti-patterns:**
+  - Abandoned: "refactor: migrate webhooks page to coss/ui components (#27714)" (4 files deleted including EventTypeWebhookListItem.tsx, WebhookListItemSkeleton.tsx, WebhookListSkeleton.tsx)
+  - Abandoned: "refactor: extract dedicated @calcom/i18n package (#28141)" (5 files deleted including next-i18next.config.js, next-i18next.config.js, next-i18next.config.ts)
+  - Abandoned: "docs: declare credentials and environment variables in calcom-api skill (#28047)" (8 files deleted including SKILL.md, authentication.md, bookings.md)
+- **Active development:** Most active areas in the last 30 days: packages/ (392 changes), apps/ (269 changes), .github/ (16 changes), specs/ (14 changes), docs/ (9 changes). Expect ongoing changes here.
+- **Fragile code:** Files that required many rapid edits (hard to get right): apps/web/public/static/locales/en/common.json (11 edits in one week); apps/web/modules/bookings/components/BookingDetailsSheet.tsx (8 edits in one week); docs/api-reference/v2/openapi.json (6 edits in one week)
+
+## What to Add Manually
+
+The most valuable context is what only you know. Add:
+
+- Architectural decisions and why they were made
+- Past incidents that shaped current conventions
+- Deprecated patterns to avoid in new code
+- Domain-specific rules or terminology
+- Environment setup beyond what .env.example shows
